{"tid":879392,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你由一開始就肯坦白","createTime":"2018-10-28T02:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T10:53:42.000Z","uid":167739,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"588856c0613fec5af505f13259a391041356d53f","tid":879392,"uid":167739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T02:06:52.000Z","msg":"如果你從一開始就肯對我坦白一切 我一定唔會沉船<br />\n點解要係我沉左船之後先坦白？<br />\n唔知情既情況下做人第三者真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身以為可以開開心心 今年生日終於有男朋友陪我過生日<br />\n結果呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過好慶幸我自己講左分手先<br />\n因為我真係唔想做人第三者<br />\n雖然我好驚我唔會揾到另一個我咁愛佢 咁錫佢既人<br />\n但我覺得點都好過做人第三者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對你好 無人稀罕我好 無人欣賞我好<br />\n原來你習慣他一套 從來沒有愛我 看得清楚<br />\n我知道 不必得到 不妨陪襯 但願為你好<br />\n<br />\n藍絲天蠍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81b2fcb20e4a0731310e04fac6bdafce6d9eb33","tid":879392,"uid":167739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T02:07:57.000Z","msg":"每日都問自己肯醒未"},{"pid":"5b49d1ab9470dd21fe1e412c44b7c40f73f19316","tid":879392,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e81b2fcb20e4a0731310e04fac6bdafce6d9eb33","tid":879392,"uid":167739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T02:07:57.000Z","msg":"每日都問自己肯醒未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T02:09:44.000Z","msg":"咁你肯醒未?"},{"pid":"cd0e12b0acd13cc42024357f1789925fb2ca4cd4","tid":879392,"uid":143680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T02:12:10.000Z","msg":"覺得絲打好怡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢女朋友應該都好慘⋯<br />\n咩都唔知 繼續俾人呃"},{"pid":"72eed17a8944351b2c623a0499259d685a977cea","tid":879392,"uid":167739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b49d1ab9470dd21fe1e412c44b7c40f73f19316","tid":879392,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e81b2fcb20e4a0731310e04fac6bdafce6d9eb33","tid":879392,"uid":167739